✓ First run — config created: /home/jules/.kubsome/config.yaml

Quick Start
────────────────────────────────────────
kubsome              Interactive CLI
kubsome serve        API + Web UI (opens browser)
kubsome tui          Full-screen terminal dashboard
kubsome --exec "pods" Run single command (CI/CD)

Enable Features
────────────────────────────────────────
pip install kubsome       CLI + API + Web UI (installed ✓)
pip install "kubsome" → enables kubsome tui (full-screen dashboard)
pip install "kubsome" → enables everything

Inside the CLI
────────────────────────────────────────
overview     Cluster health dashboard
pods         List pods with status
logs <pod>   View pod logs
diagnose <pod> Root cause analysis
events       Recent cluster events
top pods     CPU/memory usage
security     Misconfiguration scan
help         Full command list (85+)

Aliases (type less)
────────────────────────────────────────
p=pods  o=overview  l=logs  d=diagnose  e=events  s=switch

Tips
────────────────────────────────────────
• Fuzzy matching — type partial names, Kubsome finds it
• Natural language — "why is payment failing" works
• Chain commands — pods && events && alerts
• Edit config — /home/jules/.kubsome/config.yaml


